1
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:10,960
What are you good for?

2
00:01:11,840 --> 00:01:12,440
Didn't I tell you

3
00:01:12,600 --> 00:01:13,800
to drug Mei Yanhong's tea?

4
00:01:14,280 --> 00:01:15,480
Why did Brother Bao drink it?

5
00:01:16,600 --> 00:01:17,600
I'm sorry, Sister Yuejiao.

6
00:01:17,760 --> 00:01:19,200
I really did exactly as you asked

7
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:20,880
and drugged Boss Mei's tea.

8
00:01:21,200 --> 00:01:22,040
But I didn't expect

9
00:01:22,040 --> 00:01:23,560
Brother Bao to grab it and drink it all.

10
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:25,680
There was nothing I could do!

11
00:01:26,760 --> 00:01:27,360
Idiot!

12
00:01:27,800 --> 00:01:29,160
So Brother Bao drank it.

13
00:01:29,880 --> 00:01:31,280
Couldn't you drug Mei Yanhong's tea

14
00:01:31,600 --> 00:01:32,560
and make her drink it?

15
00:01:34,040 --> 00:01:35,000
You made me lose

16
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:35,920
the chance to poison her voice!

17
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:38,600
If she gets suspicious,

18
00:01:39,360 --> 00:01:40,400
how can I take back the opera house?

19
00:01:40,400 --> 00:01:41,800
I'm sorry, Sister Yuejiao.

20
00:01:42,040 --> 00:01:42,880
I promise I won't make

21
00:01:42,880 --> 00:01:44,160
this kind of mistake again.

22
00:01:44,560 --> 00:01:45,440
Next time?

23
00:01:46,240 --> 00:01:47,040
You think there's a next time?

24
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:51,720
She got lucky this time.

25
00:01:52,760 --> 00:01:54,400
Let's see who can shield her next.

26
00:01:59,880 --> 00:02:00,960
Go make me a pot of chicken soup.

27
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:03,120
Go now!

28
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:13,160
Lord Guan above,

29
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:14,680
your faithful believer, Mei Yanhong,

30
00:02:15,040 --> 00:02:16,000
sincerely bows to you.

31
00:02:16,600 --> 00:02:18,240
May you bless Hongfu Opera House

32
00:02:18,560 --> 00:02:19,480
with everything going smoothly,

33
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:20,600
and keep everyone safe.

34
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:36,920
Senior Sister.

35
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:38,520
I specially made a bowl of chicken soup

36
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:39,400
to apologize to you.

37
00:02:39,920 --> 00:02:41,280
Please don't be mad at me.

38
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:43,600
You are Master's biological daughter,

39
00:02:44,440 --> 00:02:45,240
and my junior sister.

40
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:46,840
We are family.

41
00:02:47,440 --> 00:02:48,920
How could I be mad at you?

42
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:51,080
It's just that...

43
00:02:51,640 --> 00:02:52,400
this opera house

44
00:02:53,440 --> 00:02:54,880
is Master's life's work, after all.

45
00:02:55,440 --> 00:02:57,040
Business is already bad enough.

46
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:59,480
What you said today...

47
00:02:59,760 --> 00:03:01,280
If it ruins the opera house's reputation,

48
00:03:01,640 --> 00:03:03,440
how can I face Master?

49
00:03:04,760 --> 00:03:05,560
Senior Sister,

50
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:07,680
I was wrong.

51
00:03:08,920 --> 00:03:09,800
I know

52
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:11,880
you've always been angry.

53
00:03:12,600 --> 00:03:13,400
Back then, Master

54
00:03:13,880 --> 00:03:15,200
gave the opera house and the star performer title

55
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:16,320
all to me.

56
00:03:16,920 --> 00:03:18,200
That's what made you leave home in anger

57
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:19,680
to start your own troupe.

58
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:21,120
About this...

59
00:03:21,320 --> 00:03:22,440
If I were in your shoes,

60
00:03:23,160 --> 00:03:24,840
I would feel it was unfair too.

61
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:25,560
No, Senior Sister.

62
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:27,880
I was young and ignorant.

63
00:03:28,320 --> 00:03:29,560
I didn't understand my father's good intentions.

64
00:03:30,720 --> 00:03:32,120
But when I finally understood,

65
00:03:32,920 --> 00:03:34,000
my father had already passed away.

66
00:03:34,640 --> 00:03:36,520
I didn't even get to see him one last time.

67
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:42,280
Master always had you in his heart.

68
00:03:42,840 --> 00:03:43,480
All these years,

69
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:45,480
he kept asking around for news of you.

70
00:03:46,320 --> 00:03:47,080
Before he passed,

71
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:48,240
he even urged me

72
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:50,280
to make sure I find you and bring you back.

73
00:03:51,880 --> 00:03:52,480
It's just that...

74
00:03:53,440 --> 00:03:54,560
the opera house's business

75
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:55,640
has been bad all along.

76
00:03:56,560 --> 00:03:57,320
So I...

77
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:58,320
I know.

78
00:03:59,160 --> 00:03:59,960
I came back this time

79
00:04:00,480 --> 00:04:01,400
just to help you, Senior Sister,

80
00:04:01,480 --> 00:04:02,360
revive the opera house.

81
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:04,000
But...

82
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:07,480
I don't know if you, Senior Sister,

83
00:04:08,320 --> 00:04:09,360
are willing to let me stay.

84
00:04:09,920 --> 00:04:10,800
I already said,

85
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:12,480
we are family.

86
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:14,760
Of course I want you to stay.

87
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:16,680
We will

88
00:04:16,960 --> 00:04:17,840
work together as sisters.

89
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:18,800
From now on,

90
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:20,480
you just focus on your opera skills,

91
00:04:20,640 --> 00:04:22,000
and hone your craft.

92
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:23,560
Given time,

93
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:24,960
this opera house

94
00:04:25,120 --> 00:04:25,640
and the star performer title

95
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:26,800
will all be yours, won't they?

96
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:29,240
I knew

97
00:04:29,440 --> 00:04:30,440
Senior Sister loves me the most.

98
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:34,960
Oh, right.

99
00:04:35,680 --> 00:04:36,080
The chicken soup.

100
00:04:36,320 --> 00:04:37,080
Drink it quickly while it's hot.

101
00:04:37,520 --> 00:04:38,400
It won't taste good when it's cold.

102
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:39,520
Okay.

103
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:15,160
Yuejiao,

104
00:05:15,400 --> 00:05:16,000
I'm sorry.

105
00:05:31,840 --> 00:05:33,760
What kind of luck does Mei Yanhong have?

106
00:05:34,760 --> 00:05:35,680
Is Lord Guan really

107
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:36,600
protecting her this much?

108
00:05:37,720 --> 00:05:39,080
I refuse to believe it.

109
00:06:02,320 --> 00:06:02,760
Chuncheng

110
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:03,760
What's the situation?

111
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:05,920
I found that

112
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:07,760
the victim has two wounds.

113
00:06:08,280 --> 00:06:08,720
One

114
00:06:08,840 --> 00:06:10,000
was caused by a kitchen knife.

115
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:10,720
The other,

116
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:12,200
on the artery of her neck,

117
00:06:12,200 --> 00:06:13,480
was caused by a broadsword.

118
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:14,560
That's the fatal wound.

119
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:17,080
To kill someone,

120
00:06:17,520 --> 00:06:19,600
why use two murder weapons?

121
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:21,680
What if

122
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:24,360
there are two killers?

123
00:06:27,760 --> 00:06:28,120
Xiaochun,

124
00:06:28,520 --> 00:06:30,240
before you heard Xiao Yuejiao scream,

125
00:06:30,640 --> 00:06:32,080
did you hear any fighting inside?

126
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:35,040
When I came over,

127
00:06:35,200 --> 00:06:35,800
I only heard

128
00:06:35,800 --> 00:06:36,840
Sister Yuejiao's tragic scream.

129
00:06:37,520 --> 00:06:38,360
On your way here,

130
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:39,920
did you see anyone suspicious?

131
00:06:40,520 --> 00:06:42,040
When I heard Sister Yuejiao's voice,

132
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:43,160
I rushed over immediately.

133
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:44,640
But outside the room,

134
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:45,600
I saw Lord Guan

135
00:06:45,760 --> 00:06:46,560
swing his broadsword.

136
00:06:47,320 --> 00:06:47,880
And then,

137
00:06:48,160 --> 00:06:49,160
I fainted from fear.

138
00:06:49,160 --> 00:06:49,680
Lord Guan?

139
00:06:49,960 --> 00:06:50,480
Could it be

140
00:06:50,520 --> 00:06:51,920
the Lord Guan we worship

141
00:06:52,400 --> 00:06:53,520
in the shrine manifesting himself?

142
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:54,720
Stop talking nonsense.

143
00:06:55,320 --> 00:06:56,600
How could Lord Guan kill someone?

144
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:57,360
Boss Mei,

145
00:06:59,240 --> 00:07:00,360
since you usually

146
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:01,840
worship the statue of Lord Guan,

147
00:07:02,480 --> 00:07:03,160
why don't you

148
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:05,200
take us all to have a look?

149
00:07:19,280 --> 00:07:19,840
On the broadsword,

150
00:07:19,960 --> 00:07:20,720
there really are bloodstains.

151
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:26,280
What's going on?

152
00:07:28,320 --> 00:07:29,760
Inspector Huang, it's like this.

153
00:07:30,320 --> 00:07:32,240
It's normal for the broadsword

154
00:07:32,400 --> 00:07:33,600
in our opera house to have blood.

155
00:07:34,280 --> 00:07:35,640
Before every performance,

156
00:07:35,960 --> 00:07:38,000
we use the broadsword to kill a chicken for sacrifice.

157
00:07:40,320 --> 00:07:40,760
But

158
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:42,960
this doesn't look like chicken blood.

159
00:07:43,440 --> 00:07:44,240
Instead,

160
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:46,200
it's human blood.

161
00:07:49,960 --> 00:07:50,560
Inspector,

162
00:07:51,400 --> 00:07:52,080
that blood

163
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:53,760
is very likely mine.

164
00:07:54,320 --> 00:07:54,800
Because

165
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:56,520
when I put the broadsword away yesterday,

166
00:07:57,080 --> 00:07:57,720
I accidentally

167
00:07:58,080 --> 00:07:59,320
cut my own hand.

168
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:02,040
So the blood on this blade

169
00:08:02,520 --> 00:08:04,120
is probably mine.

170
00:08:10,320 --> 00:08:11,400
Didn't you say

171
00:08:11,520 --> 00:08:12,720
the other murder weapon

172
00:08:12,720 --> 00:08:13,680
was a kitchen knife?

173
00:08:14,480 --> 00:08:16,600
But earlier in Xiao Yuejiao's room

174
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:18,280
and in this shrine,

175
00:08:18,960 --> 00:08:20,920
I didn't see a trace of a kitchen knife.

176
00:08:21,840 --> 00:08:22,760
Since it's a kitchen knife,

177
00:08:23,640 --> 00:08:24,920
we have to look in the kitchen.

178
00:08:33,880 --> 00:08:34,360
Nobody move.

179
00:08:36,800 --> 00:08:37,960
Let me do it.

180
00:08:43,760 --> 00:08:45,440
Spirits of heaven and earth,

181
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:46,760
compass needle, show your power.

182
00:08:47,400 --> 00:08:48,600
Knowing its location,

183
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:49,520
seeking its direction.

184
00:08:49,520 --> 00:08:51,040
Guide me swiftly,

185
00:08:51,040 --> 00:08:52,480
do not be lost.

186
00:08:58,480 --> 00:09:00,320
According to the compass,

187
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:02,080
that knife

188
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:04,440
should be where there is water.

189
00:09:04,880 --> 00:09:05,360
It's here!

190
00:09:06,280 --> 00:09:07,080
Really?

191
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:13,960
It's really here.

192
00:09:16,880 --> 00:09:17,400
There's blood.

193
00:09:22,120 --> 00:09:22,320
Who's there?

194
00:09:23,400 --> 00:09:23,880
Stop!

195
00:09:26,760 --> 00:09:27,200
Stop!

196
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:29,720
You think you can run from me?

197
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:34,480
Auntie Wang?

198
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:36,360
Didn't you take the day off today?

199
00:09:37,040 --> 00:09:37,720
It's so late,

200
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:39,160
why are you here?

201
00:09:54,520 --> 00:09:54,800
Auntie Wang

202
00:09:55,360 --> 00:09:56,160
How did you injure your hand?

203
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:00,120
Where did you injure it?

204
00:10:01,360 --> 00:10:02,280
When did you injure it?

205
00:10:05,800 --> 00:10:06,680
I got this yesterday...

206
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:07,640
at home...

207
00:10:07,640 --> 00:10:08,680
while doing chores.

208
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:11,000
Injured while doing chores at home?

209
00:10:12,160 --> 00:10:12,720
Then why is it

210
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:14,440
that the knife used to kill Xiao Yuejiao

211
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:16,720
has a crack on its handle

212
00:10:17,520 --> 00:10:18,880
that matches it perfectly?

213
00:10:20,160 --> 00:10:22,360
Besides, you clearly asked for leave last night.

214
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:24,920
Why would you be out in the middle of the night,

215
00:10:25,520 --> 00:10:27,160
going to the backyard of the opera house?

216
00:10:29,400 --> 00:10:31,440
Did you stay in the opera house the whole time,

217
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:33,880
wait until nightfall,

218
00:10:35,080 --> 00:10:36,280
and kill Xiao Yuejiao?
